sentences: Kim Chan-mi (born June 19, 1996), simply known as Chanmi, is a South Korean singer, actress.
Chanmi was born on June 19, 1996, in Gumi, South Korea.
On July 30, 2012, Chanmi made her debut as a member of AOA on Mnet's M! Countdown with their debut single album, Angels' Story and the title track "Elvis".
